sellerCard.oneLiner: I'm a Full Stack MERN Web and App Developer
sellerCard.description: Focused and quick learning web and mobile app development tools with more than 7+ years of experience in programming and development for various projects and clients.

description.content:
Hello,

I specialize in scalable web applications using Nextjs 14 along with Tailwind CSS and TypeScript. I have extensive experience in creating pixel-perfect designs to code, leveraging technologies like React.js, Next.js, Tailwind CSS, and Bootstrap.


Are you in search of a Next.js 14, Tailwind CSS, and Reactjs developer? Need a responsive, top-notch web app built in Next.js with TypeScript?


Expertise:

  • Next.js
  • React.js
  • Tailwind CSS
  • Figma to React.js, Next.js
  • React JS
  • JavaScript
  • TypeScript
  • Supbase
  • Prisma
  • Postgres
  • GraphQL


Why choose me?

  • 7+ years of experience
  • 100% satisfaction guaranteed
  • On-time delivery of quality work


Note: Please contact me before placing an order. The time and cost will depend on your requirements, not according to the mentioned price on this gig.

Thanks & Regards

questionsAndAnswers.question: Turnaround time for projects?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Depends on the project's complexity, but I aim for timely delivery.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Revisions if I'm not satisfied?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, revisions are available until you're satisfied.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you integrate authentication and authorization in a Next.js application?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can implement authentication and authorization using various methods like JWT tokens, OAuth providers, or third-party authentication services. Security is a top priority, and I ensure robust authentication mechanisms are in place.
